      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHE'S A GAMER (1) pushed forward last time and boxed on to finish one length away in second over 1006m at Gulfstream Park All Weather (Synthetic). Enjoys a drop in grade so she is sure to be right there at the finish. I'MWISHINGONASTAR (3) finished fourth two runs back at Gulfstream Park All Weather (Synthetic) then improved last time out to score by 3 lengths after being prominent at the turn over 1006m at Gulfstream Park All Weather (Synthetic). Won't find this as tough so she is perfectly placed to score again. PRINCESS VERA (6) was an effortless winner last time over 1207m at this track (Dirt), scoring by 4 lengths. Should camp just off the leaders. Will be in this for a long way. ONE FINE WINE (4) returns after a spell of six-and-a-half months. Started the last campaign impressively when in the placings over 1106m at Monmouth Park. Worth plenty of thought.",
